                                                                                                                                          \n            \n    \n    \n        \n                    \n                        \n                                    \u003cdiv id=\"article-body\" itemprop=\"articleBody\"\u003e\n    \n\u003cdiv id=\"custom_block_0\"\u003e\n\n                    \u003ch3\u003eSummary\u003c/h3\u003e\n        \n            \u003cdiv\u003e    \u003cul\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        A new Live Caption update is rolling out to Pixel phones.\n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        Live Caption now adds the ability to have transparent backgrounds. \n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n                    \u003cli\u003e\n                                        This will allow users to have an option to see behind the generated captions. \n                        \u003c/li\u003e\n            \u003c/ul\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n    \n        \n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eGoogle\u0026#39;s Pixel series handsets have consistently topped our charts when it comes to the \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/best-android-phones/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ebest Android phones\u003c/a\u003e that you can buy. And while there are \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/thread/pixel-owners-why-do-you-choose-google-over-other-brands/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ea lot of good reasons to own a Pixel\u003c/a\u003e, the software features found on these devices are really a cut above what you can find from other brands. \u003c/p\u003e            \n    \n                    \n                        \n                \n    \n                                        \n    \n        \n    \n        \n                \n        \n    \u003cdiv data-include-community-rating=\"false\" id=\"02a1-4b2c-8f2824c3db45\" data-nosnippet=\"\"\u003e\n        \n        \n                        \t                \n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/how-to-use-android-live-caption/\"\u003e\n\t\n\t\u003cdiv data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/google_blog_hero-image-1.png\" data-modal-id=\"single-image-modal\" data-modal-container-id=\"single-image-modal-container\" data-img-caption=\"\u0026#34;\u0026#34;\"\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n\n\n\u003cfigure\u003e\n        \u003cpicture\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 1024px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/google_blog_hero-image-1.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/google_blog_hero-image-1.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=422\u0026amp;h=268\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/google_blog_hero-image-1.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/google_blog_hero-image-1.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=310\u0026amp;h=220\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 481px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/google_blog_hero-image-1.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/google_blog_hero-image-1.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=720\u0026amp;h=400\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n        \n                                        \n                                    \n                                                                                                                                                                            \n            \n                                                            \n            \n            \n                                        \n            \u003csource media=\"(min-width: 0px)\" data-srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/google_blog_hero-image-1.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\" srcset=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/google_blog_hero-image-1.png?q=49\u0026amp;fit=crop\u0026amp;w=432\u0026amp;h=260\u0026amp;dpr=2\"/\u003e\n                \u003cimg width=\"2096\" height=\"1179\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" alt=\"A graphic showing Google\u0026#39;s upgraded and expanded accessibility features, including Guided Frame, Magnified, Live Captions, and Live Transcribe.\" data-img-url=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/google_blog_hero-image-1.png\" src=\"https://static1.anpoimages.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/google_blog_hero-image-1.png\"/\u003e\n    \u003c/picture\u003e\n                \n    \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\n\n        \n                    \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan data-field=\"label\"\u003eRelated\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n                \n                 \n                \t\n\u003ch5\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t        \t\t\t\t\n\t\t\u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/how-to-use-android-live-caption/\" title=\"How to use Android Live Caption\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e\n\t\t\tHow to use Android Live Caption\n\t\t\u003c/a\u003e\n\t\u003c/h5\u003e\n\n                                                    \n                \t\t\t\u003cp\u003eKeep your phone on silent and without missing a word\u003c/p\u003e\n\t\n\n                    \n\n\n                \n                \n                \n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n                \t\n\n\n                \n\n                \n                \n                \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n                \n        \n        \n        \n            \u003c/div\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eOver time, accessibility features have grown, allowing more users to really enjoy and harness the power provided by smartphones. The Pixel\u0026#39;s Live Caption feature is one that really elevates the experience, adding subtitles to all media that is played on the phone. And while it was good, it\u0026#39;s now getting even better, giving users the ability to activate a small tweak that can make a world of difference. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003ch2 id=\"a-small-change-that-will-make-a-huge-difference\"\u003e\n                        A small change that will make a huge difference\n               \u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n    \n\n\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n    \n\n\u003cp\u003eThe change was \u003ca href=\"https://9to5google.com/2025/02/07/android-live-caption-background-transparency/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"\u003efirst spotted by 9to5Google\u003c/a\u003e, with users now having the ability to turn on background transparency in the Live Caption feature. Previously, users only had the choice of choosing two solid colored backgrounds, and while this was good, it did make it harder to see what was behind the captions when they were onscreen.\u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003eUsers can now experience this change by activating Live Caption, and then heading to the three-dot menu located in the lower right corner. In this section, there should be an option to activate \u003cstrong\u003eBackground transparency\u003c/strong\u003e mode. Once activated, you should see the change applied to all captions that are on the screen. \u003c/p\u003e    \n\u003cp\u003e9to5Google reports that Android System Intelligence needs to be on version 16 in order for this feature to show up. So just make sure that everything on your Pixel is updated before giving this feature a try. If you haven\u0026#39;t tried the feature before, we have \u003ca href=\"https://www.androidpolice.com/how-to-use-android-live-caption/\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ea complete Live Caption guide\u003c/a\u003e on how to use the feature on your Pixel phone. \u003c/p\u003e    \u003c/div\u003e\n    \n                \n        \n        \n\n\n        \n\n\n\n\n\n                \n    \u003c/article\u003e\n\n    \n            \n        \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
